WILLIAM J. KNOX v. PAULINE C. KNOX 31 So. (2nd) 161

June Term, 1947

June 27, 1947 Special Division A Rehearing denied July 28, 1947. Katzentine & Gramling and J. Lewis Hall, for appellant. Nestor Morales, for appellees. PER CURIAM:

Affirmed. The petition for attorney fees in this Court in this causé by counsel for appellee is hereby denied.

BUFORD, Acting Chief Justice, CHAPMAN and ADAMS, JJ., and WILLIAMS, Associate Justice, concur.
